│                                                                                            │
│ The transformation is performed by `llvm::peelLoop`, which is called from                  │
│ `LoopFullUnrollPass`. The backtrace confirms that the initial IR modification is           │
│ `SplitEdge`, which is a standard utility used to prepare the CFG for peeling by ensuring   │
│ critical edges are broken.                                                                 │
│                                                                                            │
