│ causing the miscompilation.                                                                │
│                                                                                            │
│ ### 3. Root Cause Analysis                                                                 │
│                                                                                            │
│ The root cause is a flaw in the `peelLoop` utility function in `LoopPeel.cpp`. When        │
│ `peelLoop` remaps instructions for the peeled iteration, it needs to handle PHI nodes      │
│ specially. For a PHI node in a peeled block, it should only include incoming values from   │
